{"tid":2250260,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[自煮燃發] 河北十億芯片工程爛尾","createTime":"2020-10-20T03:45:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T02:41:12.000Z","uid":224066,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"9c6bfb20d9ef1e35deb68283200b333a8efa7b12","tid":2250260,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T03:45:15.000Z","msg":"【評論員: 地方政府一窩蜂 注定失敗】<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ab6tfS9Rfd4&amp;ab_channel=%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96CABLETV%26%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9ECABLENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAb6tfS9Rfd4%26ab_channel%3D%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B7%259A%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596CABLETV%2526%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B7%259A%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259ECABLENews&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEYVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=d27213d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ab6tfS9Rfd4&amp;ab_channel=%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96CABLETV%26%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9ECABLENews</a><br />\n 位於北京中關村的集成電路設計產  業園離市中心約一小時車程，是北  京芯片研發的集中地，聚集超過6  0間相關企業。<br />\n<br />\n 園區不少地方仍然空置，但無阻當  局的決心，今年8月北京市工業芯  片創新中心正式落戶。<br />\n<br />\n 這股芯片風潮亦席捲全國，截至7  月內地註冊芯片相關企業，累計有  4萬5千多間。其中第二季的新註  冊企業，就有4千6百間、較去年  同期增長2倍有多，亦是去年全年  註冊數目的八成。<br />\n<br />\n 除了在北京這些大城市，還有不少  項目在國內二三四線城市進行。像  標榜生產世界一流芯片的河北昂揚  微電子科技有限公司，原本在四年  前斥資10億元，在石家莊一個化  工園區興建250畝廠房，生產第  八代IGBT芯片。<br />\n<br />\n 並且獲河北省政府大力支持，列為  省重點建設及省市十三五規劃重點  項目，包括提供200萬元補助金  及將估值1.6億元的30畝國有  土地使用權，以半價優惠提供。<br />\n<br />\n 但直到前年項目完成約十分一，就  因為資金鍊斷裂夭折，剩下一幢爛  尾樓。昂揚公司過去兩年亦官非不  斷，包括董事長步建康控告總經理  徐國中違反協議，把大部分資金用  於購買土地和建設寫字樓，而非生  產芯片的設備，又指徐國中騙取3  0畝國有土地。<br />\n<br />\n 不過石家莊政府稱土地是合法取得  ，不需要收回。而徐國中亦都反告  步建康沒有在限時內完成芯片研發  。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oQdEBpJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoQdEBpJ.jpg&h=05114944&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 有評論員分析近年內地多個地方響  應中央號召研發芯片，但不少是一  窩蜂開公司，欠缺所需的大量資金  及配套，注定失敗。估計未來一兩  年會有更多企業出現問題，而沒有  實力的企業最終都會被淘汰"},{"pid":"69ea58a1410ddaa2bb8433d6c4f016a49a7c3cbb","tid":2250260,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T03:46:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968205341852d77d48569d71f253a2140c5dbf47","tid":2250260,"uid":161935,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:04:28.000Z","msg":"我建議不用5納米，28納米便足夠。"},{"pid":"b0dd4102ad65292f95837b54b91ac83d400a4e54","tid":2250260,"uid":258107,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:05:34.000Z","msg":"家家戶戶捐出手機等電器<br />\n實行全民大煉芯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00039145d83eb52cc2f88ef38c5d0f62e68e3c3","tid":2250260,"uid":324629,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:06:12.000Z","msg":"果然全民大煉晶只不過係支那公司同地方正苦呃funding嘅藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce2f66d713306b236a3d0a532bef309b76ec01e","tid":2250260,"uid":12166,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:06:58.000Z","msg":"手刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a9dfec5cd9c54aa236147d509a7c0124678d296","tid":2250260,"uid":121146,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:07:22.000Z","msg":"現時光刻機數目: 0 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e701f52814c16173359650e6daa07f2a293871e0","tid":2250260,"uid":151074,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:17:07.000Z","msg":